{"tid":1689923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出到黎可唔可以緊張少少 審時度勢..","createTime":"2019-11-03T05:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T13:09:02.000Z","uid":321618,"like":88,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"76f6f66614aeddf14b48d5829d730c1840a6ece5","tid":1689923,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:22:22.000Z","msg":"前排嗌曬需要物資 索帶手套first aid 做曬手勢<br />\n後面班人就係咁<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">嗌口號</span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">越嗌越hyper 唔停添㗎喎</span><br />\n想傳物資 幫手搵物資都聽唔到.. 有啲躁..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打唔過要慢慢退 前面比signal後面<br />\n哨兵嗌到聲都沙 邊度防暴落地<br />\n都仲有人一路慢慢行 一路叫口號.. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有用資訊<span style=\"color: red;\">完全</span>傳唔到去後面</span><br />\n後面包抄又傳唔到上前提水..<br />\n<br />\n同埋 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">原本無狗都比你吸引曬注意過黎啦</span><br />\n你無gear街坊裝無壓力 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你周圍嘅手足有文具 full gear啊！！</span></span><br />\n因為保護後排 比狗咬你過唔意得去.. <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">見到隔離街有狗 手足匿埋真係好心痛</span><br />\n<br />\n乖 留番啖氣 有狗就幫手嗌方向數量 行快啲<br />\n<br />\n好唔好？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾次都係咁 有啲躁..<br />\n忍唔住出post 希望唔好俾人話分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人 萬事小心"},{"pid":"de4420c5ed6167933416b08ef471a85191afd738","tid":1689923,"uid":321618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"空氣推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口號可以振奮士氣 <br />\n但希望大家啱嘅時候做啱嘅嘢"},{"pid":"5244f92eb434112df87a54f44cb0f02e01119bb4","tid":1689923,"uid":262146,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/daWoJsy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi